main event: A witness in Corpus Christi, Texas on July 28, 1959, reported observing a possible UFO that might have been Venus and was captured on film.
interesting points: Dr. Hynek analyzed frames received from a witness in Corpus Christi, Texas,The image that appeared on the frames was confirmed as real,The witness's footage captured daytime visibility of Venus,The report includes a conclusion that the object could be a light on an aircraft,The case lacked sufficient data for proper evaluation, as indicated in the report.
sighted object: possible UFO that may have been Venus
